author: BBC
title: Will Labour MPs back George Osborne and support fiscal plan?
text:
Media playback is unsupported on your device Will Labour MPs back George Osborne and support fiscal plan? 14 October 2015 Last updated at 10:07 BST
The Chancellor George Osborne is urging moderate Labour MPs to vote in favour of his fiscal plan which would balance the books for future governments.
His appeal follows a fallout within Labour after shadow chancellor John McDonnell said the party would no longer support the proposal.
Carole Walker reports from Westminster.
.
